    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069140/extras/bd407a156cb67b0265be525ee237d5d8.poster.avif?t=1763394934\" width=600 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069140/extras/bd407a156cb67b0265be525ee237d5d8.webm?t=1763394934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069140/extras/bd407a156cb67b0265be525ee237d5d8.mp4?t=1763394934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>准备好在混乱的物理沙盒中体验多米诺骨牌的狂野和过度杀伤力吧！<br><br>爆炸、连锁反应和彻底的疯狂是你所期待的。Dumbino 采用了多米诺骨牌这一简单的概念，并将其提升到一个疯狂的水平！<br><br>用疯狂的结构和创造性或混乱的解决方案来破坏大规模的多米诺骨牌，让你的大脑大开眼界！在关卡编辑器中尽情发挥你的创造力或疯狂。组装、摧毁、提示并与社区分享您的作品！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069140/extras/5f39d502919f90430a980516a4df0d01.poster.avif?t=1763394934\" width=670 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069140/extras/5f39d502919f90430a980516a4df0d01.webm?t=1763394934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069140/extras/5f39d502919f90430a980516a4df0d01.mp4?t=1763394934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特殊高菲多米诺骨牌</strong></h2>解锁各具特色的疯狂多米诺骨牌，引爆多米诺骨牌，进入一个绝对混乱的世界！多米诺骨牌不仅会倒下，还会爆炸、弹射并引发最疯狂的连锁反应。准备好用过于复杂的结构让你大吃一惊吧，并为接下来的大混乱做好准备！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069140/extras/054fa21c722a66135c9ad824896e8095.poster.avif?t=1763394934\" width=670 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069140/extras/054fa21c722a66135c9ad824896e8095.webm?t=1763394934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069140/extras/054fa21c722a66135c9ad824896e8095.mp4?t=1763394934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>单人游戏</strong></h2>在 Dumbino 中，您可以通过一个灵活的、包含多种工具和多米诺骨牌的建筑系统来创建自己的解决方案！游戏的物理系统为您提供了令人深感满意的建筑和模拟体验，无论您是作为破坏大师大肆破坏，还是看着自己的计划滑稽地崩溃，直到最终找到自己的方向。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069140/extras/a04204302a8f50ed48aed29c15904845.poster.avif?t=1763394934\" width=670 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069140/extras/a04204302a8f50ed48aed29c15904845.webm?t=1763394934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069140/extras/a04204302a8f50ed48aed29c15904845.mp4?t=1763394934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>构建、打破和分享！</strong></h2>在关卡编辑器中尽情发挥你最天马行空的想法。建造最离谱的多米诺骨牌建筑或违背逻辑的宏伟结构。然后，与社区分享您的混乱作品，让他们欣赏您最独特的杰作或最令人着迷的失误！<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在充满疯狂的活动中，多米诺骨牌破坏会带来数小时混乱、呆萌和搞笑的游戏体验<br></li><li>5个疯狂世界，各具特色，比上一个更疯狂<br></li><li>超乎寻常的物理效果，数十种物体让多米诺骨牌倒塌更加疯狂<br></li><li>为最狂热、最混乱的玩家提供众多挑战<br></li><li>社区内容，关卡编辑器潜力无限！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>准备好迎接混乱了吗？</strong></h2>如果您正在寻找一款离奇、混乱、完全夸张的多米诺骨牌游戏，那么 Dumbino 就是您的不二之选。炸开一切，让疯狂开始吧！<br><br></li></ul>",
